    <section id="founder">
      <div class="row py-3">
        <h1><strong><%= phrase('About |') %></strong></h1>
        <h2 class="pl-4" style="align-self: center"> <%= phrase('Our Founder') %> </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col tutors">
          <div class="pr-3" style="float: left;">
            <%= image_tag 'Alex Abisheganaden.png', size: '200x200', class: 'rounded-circle' %>
          </div>
          <div class="h4">
            <%= phrase('Our Founder: Mr Alex Abisheganaden') %>
          </div>

          <p> <%= phrase('hey') %>
            Mr. Alex Abisheganaden is the founder and Honorary Conductor of GENUS. In 1986, he introduced the concept of
            Niibori guitars to the Ensemble. Since then, Niibori guitars have gained immense popularity in the
            Singaporean music scene.
          </p>
          <p> <%= phrase('Having excelled as a guitarist, singer, double bassist, conductor and actor in dramas, musicals and operas,
                  Mr. Abisheganaden is one of Singapore\'s best-known musicians and stage personalities. In addition, he has
                  shown other facets of his talent as a writer, composer and music adjudicator. Some of his famous works
                  include "Huan Ying-Vanakam" and "Gela-Nexus" (Amalgamation of GENUS and his name), both of which were
                  performed by GENUS in Singapore and Germany in 2007. Mr. Abisheganaden also founded the Singapore Classical
                  Guitar Society in 1967 and remained at its helm for 25 years.') %>

          </p>
          <p> <%= phrase('In 1988, in recognition of his leadership and involvement in music in Singapore as a performer, teacher,
            adjudicator and impresario, he was awarded our government’s prestigious Singapore Cultural Medallion award.
            Apart from this award, Mr. Abisheganaden also received the COMPASS Meritorious Award from the Composers &
            Authors Society of Singapore.') %>
          </p>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="tutors">
      <div class="row py-3">
        <h1><strong><%= phrase('About |') %></strong></h1>
